
login ot Heroku:
heroku login

Create an app on Heroku:
heroku create

Deploy your code:
git add .
git commit -m "Demo"
git push heroku master

Ensure that at least one instance of the app is running:
heroku ps:scale web=1

open the website as follows:
heroku open

View information about your running:
heroku logs --tail

check how many dynos are running:
heroku ps

start your application locally:
npm install
heroku local web
go to http://localhost:5000
quit with control + C

